title: Shapeways 3D Printing Service
description: Shapeways is a popular online 3D printing service that offers a wide range of materials, including plastics, metals, and ceramics. They provide high-quality prints suitable for prototyping, product design, and customized items.

title: i.materialise 3D Printing
description: i.materialise provides a user-friendly platform for 3D printing services. They support a variety of materials, such as plastics, metals, and resins. The service is suitable for both professional and hobbyist projects.

title: Sculpteo 3D Printing Service
description: Sculpteo offers a versatile 3D printing service with a range of materials, including plastics, metals, and ceramics. They provide an online platform for easy file uploading and customization, making it suitable for both individuals and businesses.
